OL,6,FA mother accused of murdering her
OL,7,Fthree-year-old son has denied that he
OL,8,Fwas an "inconvenience" and that she
OL,9,Flost her temper before violently
OL,10,Fshaking him.
OL,12,FChristina Robinson, 30, denies murder
OL,13,Fand child neglect following the death
OL,14,Fof her son Dwelaniyah at the family
OL,15,Fhome at Bracken Court, Ushaw Moor,
OL,16,FDurham, in November 2022.
