OL,3,CMum accused of murdering son, three,
OL,4,Cdenies he was an 'inconvenience'
OL,6,FShe is also accused of deliberately
OL,7,Fscalding the little boy's legs and
OL,8,Fbuttocks in extremely hot water as a
OL,9,Fpunishment for soiling himself, around
OL,10,Fthree weeks before his death.
OL,12,FRobinson, originally from Tamworth,
OL,13,FStaffordshire, has told jurors during
OL,14,Fcross-examination that the boy was
OL,15,Faccidentally burned while she washed
OL,16,Fhim in the shower.
OL,18,FOn Thursday (14 March), Richard Wright
OL,19,FKC, prosecuting, pointed out that she
OL,20,Ftook 19 minutes to call 999 after her
OL,21,Fson collapsed on 5 November.
