OL,3,CMum accused of murdering son, three,
OL,4,Cdenies he was an 'inconvenience'
OL,6,FHe said that before contacting the
OL,7,Femergency services, she first
OL,8,Ftelephoned her husband who was working
OL,9,Faway, and conducted two internet
OL,10,Fsearches on what to do.
OL,12,FRobinson said she was still able to
OL,13,Fattend to her son, clearing his airway
OL,14,Fand putting him in the recovery
OL,15,Fposition before she dialled 999.
OL,17,FMr Wright said Robinson shook
OL,18,FDwelaniyah after losing her temper,
OL,19,Fadding: "You had had enough of that
OL,20,Flittle boy who was an inconvenience to
OL,21,Fyou."
