OL,3,CMum accused of murdering son, three,
OL,4,Cdenies he was an 'inconvenience'
OL,6,FShe replied: "Not at all, he was never
OL,7,Fan inconvenience."
OL,9,FMr Wright suggested she delayed
OL,10,Fcalling 999 because she was trying to
OL,11,Fhide the fact she had burned her son
OL,12,Fpreviously, and shook him on the day
OL,13,Fhe died.
OL,15,FHe said to her: "Even when he was
OL,16,Fdying, you put yourself first."
OL,18,FShe replied: "That's not why I didn't
OL,19,Fcall 999. It was a heated situation."
